      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>LYF香瓜子葵花子春节特惠</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #D0021B;\n            --secondary-color: #FFD700;\n            --light-color: #F4F4F5;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--light-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header, section, main, nav, aside, footer, div {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n        }\n\n        .product-detail {\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n        }\n\n        .product-detail h2 {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .price-box {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: flex-start;\n            align-items: baseline;\n            background-color: var(--light-color);\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .price-box p:first-child {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-right: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .price-box p:last-child {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            text-decoration: line-through;\n            color: #888;\n        }\n\n        .promo-banner {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .channel-entry {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 1rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .channel-entry button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .channel-entry select {\n            padding: 0.5rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .cart-panel {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin: 1rem auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .cart-panel h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .category-list {\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--light-color);\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n        }\n\n        .category-list h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .category-list ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        .category-list ul li {\n            padding: 0.5rem 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n\n        .coupon-section {\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .coupon-section h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .price-box {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: flex-start;\n            }\n\n            .channel-entry {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>LYF香瓜子葵花子，欢庆春节好味道</h1>\n        <p>香脆口感与节日喜庆相融合，品味舌尖上的团聚</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <main class=\"product-detail\">\n        <h2>规格齐全·多重组合装</h2>\n        <p>源自优质产区的葵花子，颗粒饱满，精选原料，保留天然香味，搭配节日组合装满足不同人群的喜好</p>\n        <div class=\"price-box\">\n            <p>¥39.9</p>\n            <p>¥59.9</p>\n        </div>\n        <aside class=\"promo-banner\">\n            <p>限时促销·春节专享</p>\n            <p>剩余时间：2天  库存紧张</p>\n        </aside>\n    </main>\n\n    <nav class=\"channel-entry\">\n        <button>立即购买</button>\n        <select>\n            <option>数量 1</option>\n            <option>数量 2</option>\n            <option>数量 3</option>\n        </select>\n    </nav>\n\n    <aside class=\"cart-panel\">\n        <h3>购物车</h3>\n        <p>您已选择：LYF香瓜子葵花子 组合装 × 2</p>\n    </aside>\n\n    <section class=\"category-list\">\n        <h3>相关零食分类</h3>\n        <ul>\n            <li>坚果类</li>\n            <li>糖果类</li>\n            <li>饼干类</li>\n            <li>果干类</li>\n        </ul>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"coupon-section\">\n        <h3>领取优惠券</h3>\n        <p>满99减20，限春节期间领取</p>\n    </section>\n</body>\n</html>"
